<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Modern Internship Resume</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .resume-container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .left-section {
            width: 35%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f1f1f, #4b5563);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .right-section {
            width: 65%;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f1f1f;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #4b5563;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
        }
        .contact-item, .skill-item, .edu-item, .exp-item {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .profile-img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 4px solid #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .social-links a:hover {
            color: #d1d5db;
        }
        h2, h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        p, li {
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .resume-container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .left-section, .right-section {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="resume-container">
        <!-- Left Section: Personal Details -->
        <div class="left-section">
            <img src="<%=profileImage%>" alt="Profile Picture" class="profile-img">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Sapna Raj</h2>
            <p class="text-sm mb-6">Aspiring Legal Professional</p>

            <div class="contact-item">
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Contact</h3>
                <p>Email:ssapnashree@gmail.com</p>
                <p>Phone:+917634896724</p>
                <p>Location:Noida,sector 76</p>
            </div>

            <div class="skill-item">
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Skills</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm">
                    <li>Legal Research & Analysis</li>
                    <li>Contract Drafting</li>
                    <li>Case Management</li>
                    <li>Communication & Negotiation</li>
                    <li>MS Office Suite</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Section: Educational & Professional Details -->
        <div class="right-section">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Professional Summary</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Dedicated and detail-oriented legal professional with a strong academic background in law, having completed LLB and passed the All India Bar (AIBE) Examination. Seeking an internship opportunity to apply legal research, drafting, and analytical skills in a dynamic legal environment.
            </p>

            <div class="edu-item">
                <h3 class="section-title">Education</h3>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">All India Bar Examination (AIBE)</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Bar Council of India</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">2025</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Bachelor of Laws (LLB)</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">RPS Law College Patna</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">2021 - 2024</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Master of Arts in Political Science</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Lalit Narayan Mithila University</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">2018-2020</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">Bachelor of Arts in Political Science</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">BhimRao Ambedkar University</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">2013 - 2016</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="exp-item">
                
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li>Passed the All India Bar Examination on first attempt (2025)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>